SCP-2605-1 instances have an internal temperature of approximately 51 degrees Celsius
附加记录：    

Agreeing with Scantron on this. You can say that they are isolated regions in space that have the constant temperature of 51º C and do not undergo convection.




Pros:

Although 2605-1 should be one person, why are there multiple instances of it around? There're potentially interesting implications to work with here.


Cons:

As mentioned above, it's hard to swallow vacuum with temperature. And since that is not really vacuum in the end, it could be phrased as something else.


Verdict: Neutral vote







